title: TASM Bonus Featurettes (2012-2014)
description:
Here's the two exclusive featurettes for both installments of the TASM movies, which i'm sure haven't been uploaded online to date. I'm sure the bonus disc for the first film may not be readily available these days, but the one for TASM2 is probably easier to find due to it being recently released, but it's here as well for anyone interested.

Enjoy!
